                    <span class="twitter sr-social-btn" data-url="https://theweek.com/speedreads/909607/dr-phil-begrudgingly-apologizes-comparing-coronavirus-swimming-pool-deaths" data-text="Dr. Phil begrudgingly apologizes for comparing coronavirus to swimming pool deaths" ></span>
                    <a class="email sr-social-btn" href="mailto:?subject=Dr. Phil begrudgingly apologizes for comparing coronavirus to swimming pool deaths&amp;body=https://theweek.com/speedreads/909607/dr-phil-begrudgingly-apologizes-comparing-coronavirus-swimming-pool-deaths" title="Share by Email" aria-label="Share by Email"></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

