    <section class="page-1 section-8 sr-story-main sr-last" id="909461">
        <article class="sr-story clearfix" data-id="909461" data-url="/speedreads/909461/hugh-jackman-wasnt-available--nudge-nudge-wink-wink--star-cats" data-headline="Hugh Jackman 'wasn't available' — nudge nudge wink wink — to star in Cats" data-tags="[speedread,News,Lifestyle]" data-publish-date="April 17, 2020" data-authors="[Jeva Lange]">
            
            
                            <div class="sr-slug"><a href="/speedreads/section/we%20won%27t%20tell">we won't tell</a></div>
            
            <div class="sr-headline-section">
                <div class="edit-link">
	<a href="http://cms.theweek.com/admin/tw-admin/edit/909461">Edit</a>
</div>                <h2 class="sr-headline"><a href="/speedreads/909461/hugh-jackman-wasnt-available--nudge-nudge-wink-wink--star-cats">Hugh Jackman 'wasn't available' — nudge nudge wink wink — to star in <em>Cats</em></a></h2>
            </div>

            <div class="sr-date">2:27 p.m.</div>

            <div class="sr-body-share-wrapper">
                <div class="sr-body" id="sr-body-909461">
                                            <div class="sr-image-section">
                            <a href="/speedreads/909461/hugh-jackman-wasnt-available--nudge-nudge-wink-wink--star-cats" tabindex="-1">
                                    
    
                
        
                

                
                
                
                
        
    <picture class="picture-wrapper sr-image">    <source srcset="" type="image/webp"/>        <img class="picture webpLazyInView" alt="Hugh Jackman turned down a role in Cats." src="/bundles/twsite/images/empty-src.png" data-image="https://images.theweek.com/sites/default/files/styles/tw_image_6_4/public/gettyimages-1132368586.jpg?itok=0CeNIZ-r&resize=180x180"
                                            />
    </picture>
                                <div class="sr-image-credit">Phil Walter/Getty Images</div>                            </a>
                        </div>
                    
                    <div class="sr-text">
                         <p>Hugh Jackman has at last admitted that director Tom Hooper offered him a role in the "<a href="https://www.thewrap.com/cats-film-review-musical-movie-2019-taylor-swift/" target="_blank">jarring fever dream</a>" that was 2019's <em>Cats</em>. Asked directly <a href="https://www.thedailybeast.com/hugh-jackman-on-his-closeted-con-artist-in-bad-education-and-turning-down-cats" target="_blank">by <em>The Daily Beast</em>'s Marlow Stern</a> if he turned down a role, Jackman replied: "Umm … yep."</p>
<p>Although Jackson earned an Academy Award nomination for his work with Hooper on <em>Les Misérables</em> in 2012, it apparently wasn't enough to sell him on Hooper's follow-up musical, which has since been described as "<a href="https://www.mirror.co.uk/film/cats-most-brutal-reviews-film-21127541" target="_blank">the worst thing to happen to cats since dogs</a>." When pressed on what role he was offered, Jackman said, "there were a couple of options there based on availability and time, and I really … yeah, I just wasn't available at the time."</p>
<p><em>Suuuuure</em>. Read <a href="https://www.thedailybeast.com/hugh-jackman-on-his-closeted-con-artist-in-bad-education-and-turning-down-cats" target="_blank">the full interview at <em>The Daily Beast</em>.</a> <a class="author" href=/authors/jeva-lange><em>Jeva Lange</em></a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="speedreads-share-section sr-909461">
                    <span class="fb sr-social-btn" data-url="https://theweek.com/speedreads/909461/hugh-jackman-wasnt-available--nudge-nudge-wink-wink--star-cats" data-text="Hugh Jackman 'wasn't available' — nudge nudge wink wink — to star in Cats"></span>
                    <span class="twitter sr-social-btn" data-url="https://theweek.com/speedreads/909461/hugh-jackman-wasnt-available--nudge-nudge-wink-wink--star-cats" data-text="Hugh Jackman 'wasn't available' — nudge nudge wink wink — to star in Cats" ></span>
                    <a class="email sr-social-btn" href="mailto:?subject=Hugh Jackman 'wasn't available' — nudge nudge wink wink — to star in Cats&amp;body=https://theweek.com/speedreads/909461/hugh-jackman-wasnt-available--nudge-nudge-wink-wink--star-cats" title="Share by Email" aria-label="Share by Email"></a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </article>

